usage scenarios
===============

* group all probe systems in a cluster together
  * root proberef refers to each system
  * e.g. all webserver hosts

* group all probes of a particular type
  * e.g. load probe for all hosts in a network

* group all probe systems with a specific scheme
  * e.g. all AWS instances

* combinations of the above groupings
  * e.g. load probes for webservers which are AWS instances

* ad-hoc ephemeral groupings
  * e.g. sysadmin creates a short-lived group for hosts which were affected by a particular issue
